566
00:22:51,640 --> 00:22:52,480
2 years ago

567
00:22:52,680 --> 00:22:53,759
and went to work at Xuanyi.

568
00:22:54,400 --> 00:22:55,160
That's when you met,
right?

569
00:22:57,400 --> 00:22:59,200
My brother got a fever when he was a kid,

570
00:22:59,559 --> 00:23:01,079
which affected his hearing.

571
00:23:01,359 --> 00:23:02,000
He later kept

572
00:23:02,000 --> 00:23:03,279
wearing a hearing aid all the time, right?

573
00:23:03,920 --> 00:23:05,079
So it's harder for him

574
00:23:05,119 --> 00:23:06,759
to find a job compared to other people.

575
00:23:07,519 --> 00:23:09,200
He's loved tinkering with electronics

576
00:23:09,200 --> 00:23:09,960
since he was a kid,

577
00:23:10,319 --> 00:23:11,759
so I set up a repair shop for him.

578
00:23:12,200 --> 00:23:13,559
That way he could make a living,

579
00:23:13,680 --> 00:23:14,480
and do something

580
00:23:14,480 --> 00:23:15,839
he actually interested in.

581
00:23:17,200 --> 00:23:18,119
Back then,

582
00:23:18,240 --> 00:23:19,440
