583
00:23:19,640 --> 00:23:20,440
There was a thug

584
00:23:20,480 --> 00:23:22,039
who saw how young we siblings were

585
00:23:22,440 --> 00:23:23,599
and came to cause trouble every day.

586
00:23:23,920 --> 00:23:25,160
Just then, Xing Wu came by

587
00:23:25,160 --> 00:23:25,960
looking for work.
Without saying a word,

588
00:23:26,960 --> 00:23:27,640
he chased them off
and protected us.

589
00:23:31,200 --> 00:23:31,920
Yeah.

590
00:23:32,039 --> 00:23:33,160
Someone like Xing Wu,

591
00:23:33,519 --> 00:23:35,359
usually looks quiet and reserved,

592
00:23:35,799 --> 00:23:37,240
but he's quite fierce when he fights.

593
00:23:37,680 --> 00:23:38,519
Exactly.

594
00:23:38,960 --> 00:23:41,119
He's just a man of few words,

595
00:23:41,599 --> 00:23:42,799
keeping silent usually.

596
00:23:42,960 --> 00:23:44,119
But whatever he promises you,

597
00:23:44,279 --> 00:23:45,079
he'll definitely do.

598
00:23:46,720 --> 00:23:47,920
I lost my parents early.

599
00:23:48,480 --> 00:23:49,920
For us siblings, meeting Xing Wu

600
00:23:49,920 --> 00:23:50,839
felt like

601
00:23:51,400 --> 00:23:52,359
gaining another family member.

602
00:23:56,119 --> 00:23:57,279
It's the same for me.

603
00:23:58,799 --> 00:23:59,720
This year,

604
00:23:59,759 --> 00:24:01,359
Shunyi has basically been

605
00:24:01,359 --> 00:24:02,839
