606
00:24:03,319 --> 00:24:03,839
He's

607
00:24:04,200 --> 00:24:05,559
capable, does great works,

608
00:24:05,599 --> 00:24:06,279
always responds to requests.

609
00:24:06,319 --> 00:24:07,559
He's earned me a lot of money.

610
00:24:07,720 --> 00:24:08,599
And He and I are great
business partners.

611
00:24:09,920 --> 00:24:11,079
Just business partners?

612
